      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended for those looking for a project or a source for parts. It has significant mechanical issues that will require professional attention to be roadworthy again, and the body shows heavy wear, including deep scratches and noticeable rust. The interior is also in rough shape with several tears in the upholstery. It's a fixer-upper, but it could be a valuable resource for the right buyer.",
