    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really great shape\u2014I've taken excellent care of it, and it still runs like a dream! It's perfect for weekend getaways or just zipping around town in comfort. You\u2019re going to love how smooth it feels on the road. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make someone else very happy. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the high-revving S54B32 power plant, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Mated to a sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual, the drivetrain is mechanically sound with a recently refreshed VANOS system and reinforced rear subframe mounting points. The suspension benefits from updated bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining the chassis's legendary handling characteristics. While the aesthetics show minor signs of use consistent with a 'good' rating, the performance envelope remains intact, offering a visceral, analog experience for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. No mechanical issues. Firm price.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2019 Lexus RX 350 in Eminent White Pearl, a vehicle that perfectly balances premium comfort with legendary reliability. This SUV has been a dependable family vehicle, maintained strictly according to the factory schedule with a full set of service records available for your review. The V6 engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly, providing that signature quiet Lexus ride. The interior is finished in Parchment leather with Espresso walnut trim; while you will notice some light creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster and a few faint scuffs in the cargo area, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. All technology features, including the blind-spot monitoring, heated seats, and the power liftgate, are in perfect working order. Externally, the car shows beautifully with a deep metallic flake, though I want to be fully transparent: there is one small door ding on the rear passenger side and a few minor rock chips on the front bumper from highway driving. The tires are at about 60% life, and the brakes were serviced last fall. This is a solid, honest car that looks great and drives even better, ready for its next owner to enjoy for years to come.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a distinguished balance of performance and reliability. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a refined driving experience supported by consistent mechanical integrity. A premier selection for the discerning driver, this model provides exceptional value and long-term dependability without compromise.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable, clean, and runs like a dream! It\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready to hit the road with a new owner who will appreciate it just as much as I have. Come take it for a spin, you\u2019re gonna love how it feels!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a 1993 Mazda RX-7 FD3S, a masterclass in front-midship balance and power-to-weight efficiency. Power is delivered by the iconic 13B-REW twin-rotor engine, featuring a sequential twin-turbocharger system that maintains boost pressure with surgical precision through the power band. This specimen retains its factory 50/50 weight distribution and sophisticated four-wheel double-wishbone suspension, offering tactile feedback and high lateral G-force stability. Mechanical updates include a high-capacity aluminum radiator and silicone vacuum line replacement to mitigate heat-cycle fatigue common to the platform. The 5-speed manual transmission exhibits crisp synchronization, and the limited-slip differential provides predictable lock-up under load. The chassis is structurally sound with no evidence of fatigue or oxidation on the subframes. While the exterior shows minor aerodynamic wear consistent with a driven machine, the drivetrain remains tight and the apex seal compression is well within factory tolerances.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
